trans-unit.source: Contains the service's virtual path when the service is hosted in Internet Information Services (IIS) or Windows Process Activation Service (WAS).
trans-unit.target: Inneholder tjenestens virtuelle banen når tjenesten ligger i Internet Information Services (IIS) eller Windows Process Activation Service (WAS).

trans-unit.source: This extension is present only for services hosted in IIS or WAS.
trans-unit.target: Denne filtypen finnes bare for tjenestene som er vert for IIS eller WAS.

trans-unit.source: Services can determine whether they are hosted in IIS or WAS by retrieving this extension from their <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>, as shown in the following example.
trans-unit.target: Services kan fastsette om de er vert for IIS eller WAS ved å hente denne utvidelsen fra sine <xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>, som vist i eksemplet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase>

trans-unit.source: Gets the virtual path of the IIS or WAS application that hosts the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] service.
trans-unit.target: Henter som er vert for den virtuelle banen for applikasjonen som IIS eller WAS den [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The virtual path of the IIS or WAS application that hosts the service.
trans-unit.target: Den virtuelle banen for applikasjonen som IIS eller WAS som er vert for tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This method is provided to support the [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden er angitt for støtte av [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: This method supports the [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be called directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden støtter det [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] infrastruktur og skal ikke kalles direkte fra koden.
Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.ServiceHostBase"> </xref> ved hjelp av den virtuelle banen.

trans-unit.target: Henter navnet på området for applikasjonen som IIS eller WAS som er vert den [!INCLUDE[indigo2](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] tjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The site name of the IIS or WAS application that hosts the service.

trans-unit.target: Henter den virtuelle banen brukes av en tjeneste.
